            <scopecontent id="aspace_e4d3c852041d47fbf7f512a149c3814f">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Folding pamphlet advertising Lanteen birth control (diaphragm and contra-ceptive jelly) as reliable and scientifically accepted. With a discussion of unreliable methods, the economic impact of unplanned pregnancies, and lists "Medical Bureaus of Information on Birth Control" in Chicago, Detroit, and Milwaukee. Chromolithograph with illustrations, measures 170 x 80 mm folded, 170 x 310 mm unfolded. 3 copies.</p>
            </scopecontent>
         </c>
